Other forms of harm associated with abortion on women in Turkey were challenging to analyze as a series of questions regarding unwanted pregnancy, unwanted pregnancy outcomes, reproductive decision making with men, and support from men in Turkey did not occur.
The data would have provided the opportunity to capture the experience in Turkey of a woman who has an unwanted pregnancy and chooses an abortion, but has difficulty engaging a man for support.
